'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ajaymalik14/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ajaymalik14</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 16, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Plugin worked for few days than all page started showing 404 and database row column error in settings. Now my SEO is screwed</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">404 !!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dipakbbsr/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa2df914c4897c4a0080c82e90ef2912?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa2df914c4897c4a0080c82e90ef2912?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dipakbbsr/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Dipak Kumar Pusti <small>(dipakbbsr)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 29, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My template was with Avada builder, later I created another one with just default editor, both are showing 404. But in another project it worked perfectly with WP Backery Builder as well. Not consistent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Errors !</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/missizaza/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3da6641ed34f0d970065e5a4a9ba750a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3da6641ed34f0d970065e5a4a9ba750a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/missizaza/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">missizaza</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 4, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Easy to design the template and to upload the data spreadsheet. It looks great at first but then you notice errors. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am a director of a company and although I have quite a bit of programming experience, website management is not meant to be my daily job. I need to rely on a site that doesn\'t require micro-management. MGP is not working for me. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When I first designed my site with MPG I wanted to use geo-location phone numbers to target customers within a 100 mile radius. The generated pages looked ok on a desktop but when viewing on a squashed device such as mobile cell phone the number turns to the text that\'s in the template: {{mpg_phone}}. To remove this error I could use only the one phone number that\'s linked directly to the head office. This is pretty useless if you\'re trying to appear \"local\" if you have only got one area code. This means that I should rather have an 0800 number. Customers don\'t like calling 0800 numbers and a mobile number isn\'t professional. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Having to live with this fault I discovered another serious one: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A few months after I launched the site, ALL of my mpg-pages returned 404 error to google. They were non-existent. Thankfully ThemeIsle does communicate by email, and they said I should use an older version of the plugin. Time and time again I reverted back, but the issue was still there. Most times it returns a 404 error, but sometimes it\'s showing the template with a page full of {{mpg_village}} where it\'s meant to pop the data from the spreadsheet. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ThemeIsle seem to have great reviews so I bought the life-time membership. It\'s been less than a year and they are refusing a refund. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A few years back I used to use their contact form plugin Gutenberg and this thing also stopped working. So I don\'t really have much confidence in ThemeIsle. Not sure why everyone else gives them such great reviews. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">sure</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/compasscarpetrepair/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e2c0f57da3b69635c15ac1b12aa43d8a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e2c0f57da3b69635c15ac1b12aa43d8a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/compasscarpetrepair/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Wilson006 <small>(compasscarpetrepair)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 4, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">sure</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Unnecessary stuff</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gianty/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aad901871c87433daed0a6bd0a16804b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aad901871c87433daed0a6bd0a16804b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gianty/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gianty</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 27, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I thought it would be a good idea to try this plugin out. I installed it buty didn\'t create any mpg pages as I was building the site. I then ran a site crawl and got thousands of 301 redirected pages. After A LOT of searching the plugin adds a multi-cities sitemap page with all the world\'s major cities. Not only that but it adds this into robots.txt. I had to go into my database as well as ftp to try and find all this and clean it up/delete as my crawl score kept being super low with all these trash pages that were created. Yeh, basically NOT a fan. Would AVOID.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A main part of my business.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ryanleer/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/45f34e7dcd9f20b577ad73e26506fe1c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/45f34e7dcd9f20b577ad73e26506fe1c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ryanleer/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ryanleer</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 27, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is insane. It\'s complex at first, but once you get the hang out it, there are...so so many opportunities.\n\nI don\'t know code or any of that.\n\nthe help email is also great, always replies with useful info.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome service</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ashishbrst/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a08b4a4533dc56eb90f35486464eb520?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a08b4a4533dc56eb90f35486464eb520?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ashishbrst/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ashishbrst</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 4, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin..!! Amazing support from them for the questions/queries.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">very good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wael_elsaid/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/80f84cacb62653742db31fa91a386fd8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/80f84cacb62653742db31fa91a386fd8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wael_elsaid/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">wael_elsaid</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 19, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">very good one</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Absolutely fantastic!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bgarlinski/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5fa9c6d537db714904ad2d911291c5c5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5fa9c6d537db714904ad2d911291c5c5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bgarlinski/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bgarlinski</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 18, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I real \"must have\" for building a serious site and a SEO strategy. Very powerful, and the support is quick and patient even for a lamer as I am. RECOMMENDED 100%</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simply awesome</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ulisessnow/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fa54ee1fccd1e564d291f41890a1a93a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fa54ee1fccd1e564d291f41890a1a93a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ulisessnow/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ulisessnow</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 12, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Although the plugin is not perfect yet (I\'ve experienced repetead problems during external data loading via Google Sheets and when I use the generated lists inside static pages), it\'s by far the best I\'ve found.\n\nI\'ve created more than 20000 pages with MPG plugin. Now I\'m waiting the next release to be able to add a search for those pages/posts/whatever.\n\nThanks to the team, and congratulations for this great job.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:141:\"Create pages in bulk. This mass landing page creator can generate pages, bulk edit, and update pages in minutes with custom URLs and content.\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:5:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:88:\"https://ps.w.org/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=2884712\";s:7:\"caption\";s:71:\"<strong>Multiple pages.</strong> Unique and searchable URLs in minutes.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:88:\"https://ps.w.org/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2884712\";s:7:\"caption\";s:77:\"<strong>Custom URLs.</strong> Create dynamic URLs for each new page generated\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:88:\"https://ps.w.org/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2884712\";s:7:\"caption\";s:93:\"<strong>Additional sitemap generator.</strong> Create and submit a new sitemap automatically.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:88:\"https://ps.w.org/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2884712\";s:7:\"caption\";s:105:\"<strong>Dynamic Unique Content.</strong> Customize Schema, Spintax, and all other elements in your pages.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:88:\"https://ps.w.org/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=2884712\";s:7:\"caption\";s:93:\"<strong>Create inlinks.</strong> Optimize your website with internal links to your new pages.\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:30:{s:6:\"2.8.12\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.2.8.12.zip\";s:5:\"3.0.0\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"3.0.1\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"3.0.2\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"3.1.0\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"3.2.0\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.2.0.zip\";s:5:\"3.3.0\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.0.zip\";s:5:\"3.3.1\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.1.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.10\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.10.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.11\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.11.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.12\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.12.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.13\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.13.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.14\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.14.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.15\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.15.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.16\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.16.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.17\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.17.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.18\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.18.zip\";s:6:\"3.3.19\";s:85:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.19.zip\";s:5:\"3.3.2\";s:84:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/multiple-pages-generator-by-porthas.3.3.2.zip\"