/div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I found that following the recommendations and instructions leads to this plugin working very well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">bad support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/luuuuuly58/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5e46bf6c812663cb68b1826e12fe67c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5e46bf6c812663cb68b1826e12fe67c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/luuuuuly58/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">luuuuuly58</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 12, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">i had a problem with the plugin and i contacted them, after they answered me once but still their ans didnt fix my problem the quite answering after i tried twice, badd support..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Increible, facil y eficaz</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rsaez/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/322cef0475f075b345a083c26f165437?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/322cef0475f075b345a083c26f165437?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rsaez/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rsaez</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 11, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Lo que ms me gust es que no tuve que romperme la cabeza con configuraciones complicadas; lo instalas, pones tus datos de Cloudflare y listo!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/t_ed/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e71eccaf9a54c5ec7934a3431d498db9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e71eccaf9a54c5ec7934a3431d498db9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/t_ed/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">T_ed</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 10, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Easy to use, fast and reliable plugin. Definately one of the best caching plugin</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">One of the great ones..</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bluemagma/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/164ad9cf265e9a88ad807ab77abe4f53?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/164ad9cf265e9a88ad807ab77abe4f53?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bluemagma/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bluemagma</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 10, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">A little bit of setup AND built in tooling to check if Cloudflare really is caching your site! Made it so much easier to run a website on a raspberry pi out of my home internet because I could easily configure the caching for Cloudflare. 6 STARS</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">This is the best caching plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/irawibowo/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bde7cf86e5a78a7c206bba7ffedce6fb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bde7cf86e5a78a7c206bba7ffedce6fb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/irawibowo/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">irawibowo</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 9, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">This is the best caching plugin I\'ve ever used! I have Cloudflare Pro with the APO feature enabled, but I kept facing problems. Then, I tried this plugin, and everything started working smoothly. What\'s even better, this plugin is free!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Solid CF Integration with LiteSpeed</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/upstaterider/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/71109075e75cd0f603e0bde8b5f73d21?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/71109075e75cd0f603e0bde8b5f73d21?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/upstaterider/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">David Keevis <small>(upstaterider)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 31, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I\'m using this side by side with LiteSpeed cache on a LiteSpeed server, delivering on a CF free account.  While I don\'t have any customized page cache rules set up yet, everything works like a charm.  The ability to go into Dev mode without logging into CF is nice, and remaining in Dev mode whilst not logged into CF is a bonus.  It\'s a good clean capability.  I\'ll be running some testing in the future with a CF APO implementation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">great plugin and works better then default Cloudflare plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jmaartenw/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fb075d3ce49ef0083c1d002072a76847?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fb075d3ce49ef0083c1d002072a76847?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jmaartenw/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">JMaartenW</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 31, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Great plugin and works better then default Cloudflare plugin</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Makes wordpress and woocommerce super fast</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amirhmoradi/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3a1385b730ab9b3d6a6c4223f031372?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3a1385b730ab9b3d6a6c4223f031372?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amirhmoradi/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">amirhmoradi</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 29, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">This is a MUST have plugin if you want a super fast website. make sure to read all the configurations in detail to get the best use.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:96:\"Speed up a WordPress website by caching your webpages onto global CDN using any Cloudflare Plan.\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-cloudflare-page-cache/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2291994\";s:7:\"caption\";s:112:\"This screen shot description corresponds to screenshot-1.jpg\nStep 1 - Enter your Cloudflare\'s API Key and e-mail\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-cloudflare-page-cache/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2291994\";s:7:\"caption\";s:87:\"This screen shot description corresponds to screenshot-2.jpg\nStep 2 - Select the domain\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-cloudflare-page-cache/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2292001\";s:7:\"caption\";s:91:\"This screen shot description corresponds to screenshot-3.jpg\nStep 3 - Enable the page Cache\";}}s:8:\"ver