a-text {\"mediaId\":160,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=160\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/20.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-160 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Harbor (Controller)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Turkish bounty hunter, Fade, unleashes the power of raw nightmares to seize enemy secrets. Attuned with terror itself, she hunts targets and reveals their deepest fearsbefore crushing them in the dark.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":161,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=161\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/21.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-161 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Gekko (Initiator)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gekko the Angeleno leads a tight-knit crew of calamitous creatures. His buddies bound forward, scattering enemies out of the way, with Gekko chasing them down to regroup and go again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":162,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=162\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-162 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Deadlock (Sentinel)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gekko the Angeleno leads a tight-knit crew of calamitous creatures. His buddies bound forward, scattering enemies out of the way, with Gekko chasing them down to regroup and go again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->', 'Agents', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-09-19 09:50:19', '2023-09-19 09:50:19', '', 40, 'http://localhost:8800/?p=163', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
