k-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/03.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-142 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Sage (Sentinel)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The stronghold of China, Sage creates safety for herself and her team wherever she goes. Able to revive fallen friends and stave off aggressive pushes, she provides a calm center to a hellish fight.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":143,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=143\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":29} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:29% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/04.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-143 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Sova (Initiator)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Born from the eternal winter of Russias tundra, Sova tracks, finds, and eliminates enemies with ruthless efficiency and precision. His custom bow and incredible scouting abilities ensure that even if you run, you cannot hide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":144,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=144\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/05.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-144 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Viper (Controller)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The American Chemist, Viper deploys an array of poisonous chemical devices to control the battlefield and choke the enemys vision. If the toxins dont kill her prey, her mindgames surely will.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":145,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=145\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/06.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-145 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Cypher (Sentinel)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Moroccan information broker, Cypher is a one-man surveillance network who keeps tabs on the enemys every move. No secret is safe. No maneuver goes unseen. Cypher is always watching.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":146,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=146\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/07.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-146 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Reyna (Duelist)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Forged in the heart of Mexico, Reyna dominates single combat, popping off with each kill she scores. Her capability is only limited by her raw skill, making her highly dependent on performance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":147,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=147\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/08.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-147 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Killjoy (Sentinel)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The genius of Germany. Killjoy secures the battlefield with ease using her arsenal of inventions. If the damage from her gear doesnt stop her enemies, her robots debuff will help make short work of them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":148,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=148\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/09.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-148 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Breach (Initiator)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Breach, the bionic Swede, fires powerful, targeted kinetic blasts to aggressively clear a path through enemy ground. The damage and disruption he inflicts ensures no fight is ever fair.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":150,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=150\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-150 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Omen (Controller)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A phantom of a memory, Omen hunts in the shadows. He renders enemies blind, teleports across the field, then lets paranoia take hold as his foe scrambles to learn where he might strike next.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":151,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=151\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-151 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Omen (Controller)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A phantom of a memory, Omen hunts in the shadows. He renders enemies blind, teleports across the field, then lets paranoia take hold as his foe scrambles to learn where he might strike next.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":152,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=152\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/12.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-152 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Raze (Duelist)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Raze explodes out of Brazil with her big personality and big guns. With her blunt-force-trauma playstyle, she excels at flushing entrenched enemies and clearing tight spaces with a generous dose of boom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":153,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=153\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/13.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-153 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Skye (Initiator)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hailing from Australia, Skye and her band of beasts trail-blaze the way through hostile territory. With her creations hampering the enemy, and her power to heal others, the team is strongest and safest by Skyes side.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":154,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=154\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/14.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-154 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Yoru (Duelist)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Japanese native, Yoru, rips holes straight through reality to infiltrate enemy lines unseen. Using deception and aggression in equal measure, he gets the drop on each target before they know where to look.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":155,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=155\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/15.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-155 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Astra (Controller)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Japanese native, Yoru, rips holes straight through reality to infiltrate enemy lines unseen. Using deception and aggression in equal measure, he gets the drop on each target before they know where to look.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":156,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=156\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/16.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-156 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Kay/o (Initiator)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>KAY/O is a machine of war built for a single purpose: neutralizing radiants. His power to Suppress enemy abilities dismantles his opponents capacity to fight back, securing him and his allies the ultimate edge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":157,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost:8800/?attachment_id=157\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":30} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:30% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8800/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/17.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-157 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Kay/o (Initiator)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:pa